,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"790505d79ab63bb9fa042c47f6627f5aa98b98a1","tid":2498891,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a736e5e7c8d5bf91327c41955db7baffdfef1e","tid":2498891,"uid":94771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT4jLVxGgb69WbQEFCHzMLwNvyr9mKZmrZiVsh57yTW2W?filename=B90aJu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB90aJu7.jpg&h=4c525428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\"><strong><ins>【五一勞動節聯合工會活動：四月工會街站】</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n議會被廢，手足陷獄，但不代表民間就此就要消音。在今年的五一勞動節，我們對申請遊行成功再無幻想。然而，這並不代表我們放棄發聲。眾工會將在四月將會就不同議題設街站，到各區宣傳，揭露各種政府黑幕和政策問題，讓香港人看見，這一群留低的香港人，可以做到的事。<br />\n<br />\n香港的公民社會必須站在第一線，去抗衡「新秩序」的形成。工會在每個行業的身位中，「守住條線」，連結更廣泛的公民社會，是工會戰線肩負的歷史任務。<br />\n<br />\n工會亦會於街站向港人派發「揸宗旨抗暴政」卡，呼籲香港人五一以行動展示對抗決心，一息尚存，抗爭到底。<br />\n<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://t.me/unionsforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FunionsforHK&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dCNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=74eb5dc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/unionsforHK</a>"},{"pid":"0b1eaa8217e729c8d290b41527a8d982da231f59","tid":2498891,"uid":4302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:01:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2b76095028389436494f5627effbc826a7d0f7c","tid":2498891,"uid":63249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:01:51.000Z","msg":"全球最大黑社會 上線了～"},{"pid":"3fb187ed2dc87df92d38939d311b4c47debca7d0","tid":2498891,"uid":253398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ad7f6116b89a9359dc3dd0ef2db6d2d3485d96","tid":2498891,"uid":307203,"like"